snippet.title: OBSCURIA - Trailer [HD]
snippet.description:
Journey through the dark paths of Obscuria, the inner depths of the subconscious mind. And adventure shoot'em up game developed by Insiduos and powered by IPLeiria.

Game developers: Hugo Moreira
Art & music: Edgar Ferreira
Game artist: Pedro Andre
